Drop by for up-to-date business and financial news direct from CNBC, and pick up a magazine or two at the same time to carry along on your flight.

Concourse A: Open daily 4:15 a.m. until last flight departure (varies by day of the week, between 7 p.m. and 9 p.m.)

Concourse C: Open daily 4:15 a.m.-12:30 p.m.

data.name: Checkpoint Mailers
data.body: Passengers have the option of easily mailing home items not permitted on an aircraft. A shipping label is provided along with a billing form. Simply place the item in the sealable bag provided with your label and place it in the drop box. Payment options include cash or credit card.
